        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>The flared depth of the muffler outlet pipe has been increased to accept 5.5 inch pipe insertion,
                    the number of slots on the flared end has been increased to five (5), Figure 1, Item 2, and the slot
                    length increased from 1.2 inches to 2.7 inches to accommodate two (2) individual band clamps that
                    are welded (Figure 2, Item 1) in the proper position.
                </para>
                <para>Tighten the band clamps to 44 to 59 Lbf-ft (60 to 80 Nm).</para>
                <figure id="f0607031" figsize="pg-wide">
                    <graphic filename="../tsifigures/g0607031.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitheight="328px"/>
                    <caption>Figure 1. New Design Exhaust Pipe with Welded Band Clamps</caption>
                    <calloutgroup>
                        <callout1>1. Two Band Clamps Welded in Proper Position</callout1>
                        <callout1>2. Five Slots (Two Shown)</callout1>
                    </calloutgroup>
                </figure>
                <figure id="f0607032" figsize="pg-wide">
                    <graphic filename="../tsifigures/g0607032.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitheight="328px"/>
                    <caption>Figure 2. New Design Exhaust Pipe Connected to Vertical Muffler with Welded Band Clamps
                    </caption>
                    <calloutgroup>
